Package: abstractsHostParasites
Type: Package
Title: Literature Abstract Classification System
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Angel Robles
Maintainer: Angel Robles <a.l.robles.fernandez@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/alrobles/abstractsHostParasites
Description: Create abstract classification models with PU learning approach 
   using a set of abstract of an specific class and random abstracts labeled
   as unknown class. Also helps to get random abstracts from connecting
   to the 'CrossRef' 'API'. 
BugReports: https://github.com/alrobles/abstractsHostParasites/issues
